function initAccordionAutoId(){
let allAccordions = document.querySelectorAll('.accordion')
if(allAccordions){
   allAccordions.forEach((eachAccordion,acrIndex)=>{
       eachAccordion.setAttribute('id',`acr${acrIndex+1}`)
       let allAcrItemOfEachAcr = eachAccordion.querySelectorAll('.accordion-item')
       if(allAcrItemOfEachAcr){
        allAcrItemOfEachAcr.forEach((eachAcrItem,acrItemIndex)=>{
            let acrBtn = eachAcrItem.querySelector('.accordion-header .accordion-button')
            let acrCollapseBox = eachAcrItem.querySelector('.accordion-collapse')
            if(acrBtn && acrCollapseBox){
            let collpaseBoxId = `acr${acrIndex+1}-acrItem${acrItemIndex+1}-collapsebox`;
            acrCollapseBox.setAttribute('id',collpaseBoxId)
            acrCollapseBox.setAttribute('data-bs-parent',`#acr${acrIndex+1}`)
            acrCollapseBox.classList.remove('show')
            acrBtn.setAttribute('data-bs-target',`#${collpaseBoxId}`)
            acrBtn.setAttribute('aria-controls',collpaseBoxId)                            
            acrBtn.classList.add('collapsed');
            acrBtn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
            }
        })
       }
   })
}
}
